      "desc": "For students who are not required to take Area I subjects and opt not to take advanced language subjects (see footnote 1 above), all six subjects for the minor must be taken from Areas II, III, and IV, with at least one subject from each area. Students may not take more than one subject focused on the Iberian Peninsula."
